{"tid":838080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）我唔見咗條金鍊","createTime":"2018-09-27T00:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T02:12:07.000Z","uid":199983,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"69cf485d2ed95fe17efe4deb32866407d0739113","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:22:25.000Z","msg":"我琴日參加學校陶藝班除低咗手錶同手鍊，我到啱啱起身準備返學諗住戴返，但個袋入面得返隻手錶，但係我係琴晚返到屋企之後係無郁過個袋，姐係我個袋琴晚到今朝應該係原封不動，我搭車拍卡張卡係喺我手機背後，所以我都無係返屋企途中係咁喺個袋到攞嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我琴晚返屋企嘅路線係 八點幾離校到觀塘地鐵站&mdash;&mdash;〉太子&mdash;&mdash;〉美孚&mdash;&mdash;〉兆康<br />\n<br />\n我依加都去緊兆康，然後會去站務台到問有無人執過失物，無嘅我返學校校務處再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條手鍊係我媽咪比我，佢自己都戴咗好耐，我搵唔返就真係⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係唔多手鍊圖，無乜對住條鍊影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/082205_0ed05cd7841c5fc3340eac06d90928c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F082205_0ed05cd7841c5fc3340eac06d90928c0.png&h=f1d66bda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03d4d3e4c54ef3b764ebb4c025835b0637692c6b","tid":838080,"uid":130901,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"扭親手？痛唔痛呀"},{"pid":"72f25786d36dc75b12075ad00d2486ea610074e4","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"另外如果兩邊（站務同校務處）都無消息，我妟小小會去觀塘嗰邊嘅警局問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca6eab4619a583fb6032f99c336448d3cc4d54a","tid":838080,"uid":5995,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:24:32.000Z","msg":"隻手好淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c538c68baa7b2c00997f58651c670a778d2cc58e","tid":838080,"uid":208315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52cb7f8a441472ba59377d5bddeb0495af23e326","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03d4d3e4c54ef3b764ebb4c025835b0637692c6b","tid":838080,"uid":130901,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"扭親手？痛唔痛呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:24:55.000Z","msg":"唔係，影依張相係想比我個fd知我隻兔幾大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199394578ef4b79cbc1bd61e8ad611dd99a49419","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"唯一一張最清嘅圖係一樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有嘅cut咗出嚟就勁模糊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/082528_f5c7cd66fa0fefaa985906cfc69e37a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F082528_f5c7cd66fa0fefaa985906cfc69e37a7.png&h=0f587097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac1fa99c87b744f2d1a56024f4f8c02b45dd7545","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:29:22.000Z","msg":"有消息可以tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酬勞真係無乜，不過多小都會盡我能力比返小小薄籌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/whofuckingcarebae\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhofuckingcarebae&d=fiJCY29iX%2FgwfSP31nRYpdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=35bda9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whofuckingcarebae</a>"},{"pid":"306de83e6d035af260dd3e657ffec168f82a72eb","tid":838080,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cr